{{ define "about" }}
{{ template "header" . }}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-11 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card border-0">
                <div class="card-body">

                    <h5 class="card-title text-center mb-4">About This Project</h5>

                    <div class="text-start">
                        <p class="card-text">
                            This project is a <strong>learning-oriented demo application</strong> built for studying
                            distributed systems, microservices, and backend architecture.
                        </p>

                        <p class="card-text">
                            It is <strong>not a real e-commerce platform</strong> and does not involve any real
                            transactions, payments, or commercial activities.
                        </p>

                        <p class="card-text">
                            The project is developed and maintained by <strong>MoScenix</strong>, and is intended for
                            educational, experimental, and technical exploration purposes only.
                        </p>

                        <p class="card-text mb-2">
                            <strong>Technology Stack</strong>
                        </p>

                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-bordered align-middle">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th style="width: 30%;">Technology</th>
                                        <th>Introduction</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>cwgo</td>
                                        <td>A CloudWeGo toolchain for generating microservice project scaffolding in Go.
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Consul</td>
                                        <td>A service registry and discovery tool used for service registration, health
                                            checking, and service discovery.</td>
                                    </tr>

                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Kitex</td>
                                        <td>A high-performance RPC framework by CloudWeGo for inter-service
                                            communication.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Hertz</td>
                                        <td>A high-performance HTTP framework used as an API gateway or frontend
                                            service.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Bootstrap</td>
                                        <td>
                                            Bootstrap is a powerful, feature-packed frontend toolkit for building
                                            responsive
                                            web interfaces quickly.
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>MySQL</td>
                                        <td>A relational database used for persistent data storage.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Redis</td>
                                        <td>An in-memory data store used for caching and performance optimization.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Elasticsearch (ES)</td>
                                        <td>A distributed search engine for full-text search and fast query
                                            capabilities.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Prometheus</td>
                                        <td>A monitoring system used to collect metrics and observe service health.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Jaeger</td>
                                        <td>A distributed tracing system for analyzing request flows across
                                            microservices.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Docker</td>
                                        <td>A containerization platform for building and running services consistently.
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>

                        <p class="card-text text-muted mt-3 mb-0">
                            The project focuses on understanding service communication, infrastructure components,
                            and observability practices in modern backend systems.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

